race.comment: HANAFUBUKI (10) is hardly a prolific winner but what she has done is put up consistent ratings. Latest was backed up by strong closing splits that even hinted at her having something more up her sleeve and if that is the case then she can topple this lot. PROMISED LAND (2) was well fancied last time and ran up to that market expectation somewhat. Things are no tougher here though he will need a good steer from Holly Durnan from a potentially tricky draw. EXPEETEE (1) comes through the right form race along with SHULTZY (8) and the pair of them can be around the mark again. SCINTILLANTE (5) comes through a pair of good races behind a smart winner. Nothing of that level here and he is one that has shown glimpses of talent for better in the past. Real threat.
